261
00:19:49,892 --> 00:19:52,061
Nice making your acquaintance.

262
00:20:05,407 --> 00:20:08,477
What's done is done, I guess.

263
00:20:16,886 --> 00:20:19,822
I know you would have
done different.

264
00:20:22,758 --> 00:20:26,295
